  "evidence_excerpts": [
    {
      "text": "Indexed\nfolder 90 - 158\nG-103\n\nto flee (which causes the maze to change + grow)? We can't. Something must enter from outside the maze to aid us. Something must remind us, awaken us, cause us to remember (the \"legend of the Pearl\"), + thus to see the maze frozen. {illustration of a maze} My vision. The template as map of the maze - Christ as map; Acts lens / grid as map. The Grail - the maze. The blood (plasmate) in the Grail speaks to us, giving us clues to remind us. Finding the Grail equals th",
      "matched_alias": "Grail",
      "term_id": "TERM_grail",
      "term_name": "Grail",
      "term_slug": "grail"
    },
    {
      "text": "Complete\nfolder 90 - 159\nG-104\n\nocclusion, fall. However, one must realize that an irreal world is better than none at all. There is an ambiguity to our situation: it is better than hell but worse than heaven. Hell would be total encapsulation: the mind (soul) provided with no world, no \"other\" at all; so in relation to hell (no world, no other) our state is a boon, + God is guarantor of world; he has the power to compel us to assent to [representation as] world absolutely, + this is only relati",
      "matched_alias": "Paradiso",
      "term_id": "TERM_paradiso",
      "term_name": "Paradiso",
      "term_slug": "paradiso"
    },
    {
      "text": "folder 90 - 161\nG-105\n\nthen was an ascending to paradiso, world gave way to God: God outside me as world, God inside me (i.e. Valis). So to say that \"God [Valis] invaded world\" is quite wrong; this was my return to God - which is Dante's top realm. The BIP, of course, is the lowest realm, + originally I had been there. (Which is what anamnesis told me.) So my 3-74 experience of \"the second signal\" can best be understood in terms of the vertical [\"spatial\"] ascent of the \"Commedia\". Hence my impr",
      "matched_alias": "Paradiso",
      "term_id": "TERM_paradiso",
      "term_name": "Paradiso",
      "term_slug": "paradiso"
    }
  ],
